rows.label: qst201110_0010
rows.name: Oi! What are you playing at, Seori?!

rows.label: qst201110_0030
rows.name:
Please, Seori. There's no
reason for us to be fighting.

rows.label: qst201110_0040
rows.name:
I'm sorry, Seori. I'm sorry that
I can't remember who you were.

rows.label: qst201110_0050
rows.name:
But if there's one thing that's
clear, it's that you were someone
very, very special to me.

rows.label: qst201110_0060
rows.name: So let's just stop this. Please.

rows.label: qst201110_0080
rows.name:
She's deluded! Finish her off, Seori!
Don't listen to a word she says!

rows.label: qst201110_0090
rows.name:
Get Mikumari out of the way
and taking out the rest of
them'll be plain sailing!

rows.label: qst201110_0130
rows.name:
You defy the words of your
Driver? Finish her, Seori!

rows.label: qst201110_0150
rows.name: Good for nothing-! Then step aside!

rows.label: qst201110_0200
rows.name: Why... Why would you do that...?!

rows.label: qst201110_0210
rows.name:
I'm sorry, Mikumari... I never
meant for all this to happen.

rows.label: qst201110_0220
rows.name: I didn't really...want to fight you...

rows.label: qst201110_0230
rows.name: I know, Seori. I knew all along.

rows.label: qst201110_0240
rows.name:
Hey, Mikumari... Am I
going... to forget you...?

rows.label: qst201110_0270
rows.name:
Even if you forget me, I'll always
remember what you meant to me.
